      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. It has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showing no blemishes, scratches, or wear on either the exterior paint or the interior upholstery. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car comes with a complete service history documenting its preventative maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine example that is ready for a collection or immediate enjoyment.",
