    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is an absolute dream and in truly mint condition. It\u2019s been pampered in a climate-controlled garage, and the paint is still glowing! No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I've absolutely loved every mile in it, but it's time for someone else to enjoy this beauty. Come take a look\u2014you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
