    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior maintains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from rock chips, swirls, or imperfections, and has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma, preserved in a strictly smoke-free and pet-free environment. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a flawless service history with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships. It has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled setting, ensuring every rubber seal and plastic component remains as fresh as the day it was manufactured. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade example that drives with the precision and smoothness of a brand-new vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
